This directory contains a Universal Control server intended for use on a MythTV system running both a primary backend and primary frontend on the same machine. It makes use of the MythTV python bindings.

This software is provided for example purposes only, and we provide no guarantee of it being free from bugs. We do not recommend its use in any mission-critical environments.

This software is released under the terms of the Gnu General Public License version 2 and its copyright is held by the BBC.